id":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46b2fb8afd2ca25d529fc6f8b0b3c33ceaa32d02","tid":2362932,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驕傲當褒詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:22:07.000Z","msg":"驕傲作為名詞嘅時候係褒詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e79db434cb9143e5229920acedeb636d875018","tid":2362932,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2016/10/13/497857068/transcript-donald-trumps-speech-responding-to-assault-accusations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2016%2F10%2F13%2F497857068%2Ftranscript-donald-trumps-speech-responding-to-assault-accusations&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BbTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=8bb337ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.npr.org/2016/10/13/497857068/transcript-donald-trumps-speech-responding-to-assault-accusations</a><br />\n<br />\n英文版<br />\n有埋全文"},{"pid":"af65d9141983f73f096cf7931cc351a399391057","tid":2362932,"uid":333312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"This is a struggle for the survival of our nation, and this will be our last chance to save it. This election will determine whether we are a free nation or whether we have only the illusion of democracy, but are in fact controlled by a small handful of global special interests rigging the system. <br />\n<br />\nThe corrupt media in our country is no longer involved in Journalism. They are a political special interest, no different than any lobbyist or other financial entity with a total political agenda, and the agenda is not for you. It&rsquo;s for themselves. Anyone who challenges their control is deemed a sexist, a racist, a xenophobe <br />\n<br />\nThey knew they would throw every lie they could at me and my family and my loved ones. Nevertheless, I take all of these slings and arrows gladly for you. I take them for our movement so that we can have our country back. I didn&rsquo;t need to do this, folks, believe me. I built a great company and  I had a wonderful life. I could have enjoyed the fruits and benefits of years of successful business deals and business for myself and my family. Instead of going through this absolute horror show of lies, deceptions, malicious attacks <br />\n<br />\nI&rsquo;m doing it because this country has given me so much, and I feel so strongly that it&rsquo;s my turn to give back to the country that I love. I&rsquo;m doing this for the people and for the movement, and we will take back this country for you, and we will make America great again."},{"pid":"6e7606eda9969be2978fb1dac255545522ddb360","tid":2362932,"uid":324984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"Love Trump! 他一早就看得好透!"},{"pid":"a20f9fecdf435b12d2fa2f991e3d474f7b706daf","tid":2362932,"uid":31575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"704a3f151b494b9e04c2fdae8371b6f4c230d3d9","tid":2362932,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46b2fb8afd2ca25d529fc6f8b0b3c33ceaa32d02","tid":2362932,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驕傲當褒詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:22:07.000Z","msg":"驕傲作為名詞嘅時候係褒詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited